49:27.400 --> 49:29.926
Happy birthday, Gen. Dearborne.

49:30.080 --> 49:32.208
Here is your new
mobile whorehouse.

49:32.320 --> 49:34.448
Compliments of Charlie Company!

49:37.400 --> 49:39.801
Was it worth all this, Captain?
Was it worth it?

49:39.880 --> 49:40.802
I didn't know.

49:40.880 --> 49:42.848
Is it the Captain's job
to kill his own men?!

49:42.920 --> 49:45.571
- Son of a bitch!
