55:05.520 --> 55:07.568
All right, a 10?

55:08.600 --> 55:11.080
- Nine and three quarters.
- Nine and three quarters.

55:11.200 --> 55:14.522
While you're at it, write something down
and we'll get you the hell out of here.

55:14.600 --> 55:16.648
I don't want to get out of here, Dave.

55:18.600 --> 55:20.489
Al, it's true.

55:22.120 --> 55:25.010
Half of your fucking problem
is no fucking!

55:25.120 --> 55:26.087
