♫ Happy birthday to you... ♫

55:43.920 --> 55:46.969
♫ Happy birthday, General Dearborn,
Happy birthday, fuck you. ♫

55:47.760 --> 55:49.364
Hey, hey, hey, hey.

55:50.600 --> 55:53.410
Okay, okay, okay, okay!

55:53.480 --> 55:56.290
I got some money for everybody.
Hang on, baby.

55:56.920 --> 55:58.445
There you go.

56:04.760 --> 56:07.525
Sound off!
1-2...

56:12.360 --> 56:14.089
Al, look at this!

56:14.360 --> 56:16.681
Hey! It's Mickey Mouse Mantle
