- You get that bottle out of his face!

56:25.240 --> 56:28.562
Oh, my god, this boy is OD-ing
on some heavy shit.

56:28.640 --> 56:31.405
If we don't get him up right now,
he'll be cold in half an hour.

56:31.480 --> 56:33.801
All right, everybody up.
Hold on to this, Alvin.

56:34.160 --> 56:36.527
Hold on. Here we go.
Everybody up!

56:37.880 --> 56:40.690
What's this guy bringing,
potatoes in a bag?

56:40.840 --> 56:43.571
Stop fucking up. If you're not
gonna help, get out of the way!

56:43.640 --> 56:45.483
This guy's dying, goddamn it.

56:47.840 --> 56:50.320
it's over. You get down.

56:51.880 --> 56:53.041
Sandbag!

56:53.120 --> 56:56.408
The enemy blew up the General's trailer!
We'll go through over the wire!

56:56.480 --> 56:58.209
- There's VC all over the place!
- Pike!

56:58.280 --> 56:59.884
Wake up!

57:00.960 --> 57:02.291
What?!

57:02.360 --> 57:04.761
The enemy blew up
the General's trailer.

57:05.120 --> 57:08.090
All the world is exploding.
Jesus Christ!

57:10.080 --> 57:12.731
♫ Happy Birthday,
General Dearborn... ♫

57:13.320 --> 57:15.163
Jesus h. christ!

57:16.400 --> 57:18.721
Hey, Al!
Pike is sleeping like a log.

57:19.000 --> 57:21.480
Bisbee, get down,
you stupid motherfucker.

57:21.560 --> 57:23.642
Get over here and sit down.
Sit down!

57:24.400 --> 57:25.561
Pike!

57:25.640 --> 57:26.801
Oh, god...

57:27.160 --> 57:29.891
Damn it! The VC are fucking having an
attack on us, and you're out there...

57:29.960 --> 57:32.042
- playing your music.
- They're not VC.

57:32.120 --> 57:34.646
I put a Claymore
under the General's trailer.

57:37.080 --> 57:38.809
